 ###  Global view [#global-inbox]

You can view error groups for multiple entities in the global view. We understand that a team generally oversees a number of services and consolidating this information in one inbox is more effective for their workflow. 

You can group APM, Browser, Mobile, Serverless, and Otel entities together and save your curated view as a workload in two steps that take less than a minute. 

 <!-- Add IMAGE -->
 
  ###  Create a workload [#global-workload]
  
* In the dropdown menu, select the entities that you want to save as a workload and select the ‘Save as workload’ button. 
* The entities you’ve preselected will be automatically added and you have the option to add more. Select  ‘Create a workload’ once you have all the entities you need. 
* All done! View all your entities in a workload from now on.


